{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji22.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致方正平等电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致方正平等电川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月25日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我军恢复疲劳后，必须着重歼灭反动保安团队（不反动者则联络之），才能建立根据地。但目前时期不要打任何县城，以免引起大的震动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致方正平并告李先念、文建武、任质斌电的主要内容。方正平，当时任豫鄂陕军区副政治委员。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":97,"page_end":97},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}